    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561637>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Diaphorocleidus munimensis n. sp. from Bryconops cf. affinis (Characiformes, Iguanodectidae) from São José, municipality of Chapadinha and in Riacho Estrela, municipality of Anapurus, River Munim basin, Maranhão, Brazil: (a) total, ventral view; (b) copulatory complex, ventral view; (c) hook pairs 3, 4; (d) hook pairs 1,5; (e) ventral anchor; (f) dorsal anchor; (g) ventral bar; (h) dorsal bar. Scale bars: (a) 100 μm; (b) 15 μm; (c, d, g, h) 10 μm; (e, f) 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561637/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

